#: ../../source/chain/mono.rst:39 e43d72c2cd614fb1a049ba0452d1cce9
msgid ""
"This example initializes Chain Mono in scroll mode and displays the text "
"``M5STACK``. It also shows a simple controller UI on the host display and"
" uses the hardware buttons to control the Chain Mono module:"
msgstr "该示例将 Chain Mono 初始化为滚动模式并显示文本 ``M5STACK``，同时在主机屏幕上显示一个简单的控制界面，并使用硬件按键控制 Chain Mono 模块："

#: ../../source/chain/mono.rst:43 b493d7a2419d4f73b6f45a03d5b3d211
msgid "``BtnA`` toggles the scroll state between start and pause."
msgstr "``BtnA`` 在开始和暂停之间切换滚动状态。"

#: ../../source/chain/mono.rst:44 0bb6e5e03b784b68a787e88dfdda3dd1
msgid "``BtnB`` cycles the display rotation through 0, 90, 180, and 270 degrees."
msgstr "``BtnB`` 在 0、90、180、270 度之间循环切换显示旋转。"

#: ../../source/chain/mono.rst:45 744d31b770ba4b64a66225aec123a0d6
msgid "``BtnC`` cycles the display brightness level."
msgstr "``BtnC`` 循环切换显示亮度等级。"

